NK041(di)016:0: tshig bdun gsol 'debs dang 'brel ba'i bla ma'i rnal 'byor byin rlabs char 'bebs bzhugs so //
NK041(di)016:1: ah rang la lus tha mal gnas pa'i mdun mkha' ru //
NK041(di)016:2: o rgyan dri med d+ha na ko sha'i mtsho //
NK041(di)016:3: gting zab yan lag brgyad ldan chus gang ba'i //
NK041(di)016:4: dbus su rin chen pad sdong 'dab rgyas steng //
NK041(di)016:5: skyabs gnas kun 'dus o rgyan rdo rje 'chang //
NK041(di)016:6: mtshan dpe'i dpal 'bar lha lcam yum dang 'khril //
NK041(di)016:7: phyag g.yas rdo rje g.yon pas thod bum bsnams //
NK041(di)016:8: dar dang rin chen rus pa'i rgyan gyis mdzes //
NK041(di)016:9: 'od lnga'i klong nas bde chen gzi byin 'bar //
NK041(di)016:10: 'khor du rtsa gsum rgya mtsho sprin ltar gtibs //
NK041(di)016:11: byin rlabs thugs rje'i char 'bebs bdag la gzigs //
NK041(di)016:12: rgyal kun ngo bo 'chi med ye shes skur //
NK041(di)016:13: gdung shugs drag pos dad phyag rtag tu 'tshal //
NK041(di)016:14: lus dang longs spyod dus gsum dge ba'i tshogs //
NK041(di)016:15: kun bzang mchod pa'i sprin du dmigs nas 'bul //
NK041(di)016:16: thog med nas bsags sdig ltung ma lus bshags //
NK041(di)016:17: sras bcas rgyal ba kun gyi yon tan gyi //
NK041(di)016:18: khyab bdag gcig pu mgon po'i rnam thar la //
NK041(di)016:19: snying nas yi rangs dad pas gsol 'debs shing //
NK041(di)016:20: zab rgyas chos kyi char chen 'bebs par bskul //
NK041(di)016:21: rang gzhan dge ba'i dngos po kun bsdoms nas //
NK041(di)016:22: 'gro khams rgya mtsho ji srid gnas kyi bar //
NK041(di)016:23: mgon po khyod kyi rnam thar rjes bsnyegs te //
NK041(di)016:24: mkha' khyab 'gro ba 'dren pa'i don du bsngo //
NK041(di)016:25: skyabs gnas kun 'dus mkhyen brtse'i gter chen po //
NK041(di)016:26: dus ngan snyigs ma'i skyabs gcig rin po che //
NK041(di)016:27: lnga bdo'i rgud pas mnar bzhin gdung shugs kyis //
NK041(di)016:28: gsol 'debs bu la brtse bas myur du gzigs //
NK041(di)016:29: dgongs pa'i klong nas thugs rje'i rtsal phyung la //
NK041(di)016:30: mos ldan bdag gi snying la byin gyis rlobs //
NK041(di)016:31: rtags dang mtshan ma myur du bstan pa dang //
NK041(di)016:32: mchog dang thun mong dngos grub stsal du gsol //
NK041(di)016:33: zhes byas la tshig bdun gsol 'debs ci nus 'don /
NK041(di)016:34: mos gus kyis gsol ba btab pas bla ma yab
NK041(di)016:35: yum gyi sbyor mtshams dang thugs ka nas ye shes
NK041(di)016:36: kyi 'od zer sna lnga pa ba thag ltar brkyang
NK041(di)016:37: ba rang gi snying gar thim pas rgyud byin gyis
NK041(di)016:38: brlabs par bsam / badz+ra gu ru ci rigs bzla /
NK041(di)016:40: bla ma'i gnas gsum yi ge 'bru gsum las //
NK041(di)016:41: 'od zer dkar dmar mthing gsum byung nas su //
NK041(di)016:42: rang gi gnas sum thim pas sgo gsum gyi //
NK041(di)016:43: sgrib byang sku gsung thugs kyi rdo rjer gyur //
NK041(di)016:44: mthar ni bla ma 'khor bcas 'od du zhu //
NK041(di)016:45: dkar dmar thig le h'u gis mtshan pa ru //
NK041(di)016:46: rang gi snying gar thim pas bla ma'i thugs //
NK041(di)016:47: rang sems dbyer med lhan skyes chos skur gnas //
NK041(di)016:48: a +aah zhes brjod la ye nas bcos bsgyur spang
NK041(di)016:49: blang las 'das pa rang gi sems nyid gdod ma'i
NK041(di)016:50: chos sku chen po'i rang zhal blta /
NK041(di)016:51: slar yang sgyu ma lta bu'i snang ba thams cad
NK041(di)016:52: bla ma'i rang bzhin du bltas la dge ba bsngo
NK041(di)016:53: zhing shis pa brjod pas bde legs su bya'o //
NK041(di)016:54: zhes pa'ang thams cad 'dul ces pa'i gro bzhin zla
NK041(di)016:55: ba'i yar tshes brgyad la tshe rabs thams cad du
NK041(di)016:56: gu ru pad+ma'i bran du smon lam 'debs pa mi
NK041(di)016:57: pham rnam par rgyal ba'i yid kyi blo mtsho las
